Titulo: The Magic School Bus Rides Again
Enredo: Ms. Frizzle's kid sister Fiona takes the wheel at Walkerville Elementary, leading the class on wild adventures packed with science-fueled fun.
Unexpected love finds a lonely woman when she forms a connection with a humanlike hologram who looks exactly like his prickly creator.
The Pythons elevate the absurd to new heights and bring their sketches to German TV, working in phonetic German, at times with an Australian accent.
In the midnight hour, a lone DJ broadcasts the strangest – and scariest – tales from the outer edges of Kirlian, a lost city somewhere in Argentina.
Australia's toughest big-rig drivers brave wildfires, scorching deserts, treacherous downpours and chassis-deep mud to deliver their cargo on time.

Titulo: Dreamworks How to Train Your Dragon Legends

Enredo: Historical footage and interviews with soldiers showcase war stories, unique traditions and unifying principles of the Indian Army’s various regiments.
When the ghost of a woman gains a second chance at life for 49 days, she reappears in front of her remarried husband and young daughter.
From Argentina to Colombia, this stunning documentary follows five characters who share their deep connection to South America's majestic mountains.
A single dad and cosmetics brand owner figures out fatherhood on the fly when his strong-minded teen daughter moves in with him.
When mecha attack a research center, its students, pilots, and researchers must fight back with the help of mysterious artifacts and a young samurai.
Go inside the world of comedian and actor Rob Schneider in this comedy series that follows the ups and downs of his career and family life.
After her father dies and her husband goes missing, Kim Seo-hui teams up with detective Jo Tae-sik and joins the National Assembly.
Monstrous frights meet hilarious reveals on this hidden-camera prank show as real people become the stars of their own full-blown horror movie.
Paired together for an unforgettable trip across Asia, stars Lee Seung-gi and Jasper Liu become buddies as they connect with fans and local cultures.
Three teens living in the same São Paulo favela pursue their dreams while maintaining their friendship, amid a world of music, drugs and religion.
Allegations of child sexual abuse in Spain's Catholic institutions are examined in interviews with survivors, clergy, journalists and other experts.
In the wake of World War II, 11 Allied judges are tasked with weighing the fates of Japanese war criminals in a tense international trial.

Titulo: The Cat in the Hat Knows a Lot About That!
Enredo: The Cat in the Hat is back – and this time, he's teaching Sally and her brother, Nick, some awfully nifty things to think about!
Couples go on a romantic getaway to test their relationships, not knowing their families are calling the shots and cringing over their every move.
As 16-year-old Becca adjusts to her new foster home, she starts to question her reality as strange things begin to happen all around her.
Despite the Philippine government's crackdown on narcotics, high schooler Joseph expands his drug running while his cop uncle profits from corruption.
In this adult animated series, three gay co-workers lead double lives as drag queen superheroes, saving the LGBTQ community from evil nemeses.
Six strangers share a fabulous house in Tokyo, looking for love while living under the same roof. With no script, what happens next is all up to them.
This animated adaptation of the quirky four-panel comic brings the random exploits of Popuko and Pipimi to life.
Learn how to sleep better with Headspace. Each episode unpacks misconceptions, offers friendly tips and concludes with a guided wind-down.
Short films follow young adults as they navigate the gamut of emotions that come with finding romantic connection in unexpected places.
Real people's terrifying tales of the chilling, unexplained and paranormal come to life with dramatic reenactments in this reality series.
From germs and emotions to social media and more, it's the science of your world explained in a way that's refreshingly relatable.
Delve into the delectable world of Chaoshan cuisine, explore its unique ingredients and hear the stories of the people behind its creation.
Two actors and a makeup artist fight to make their own way in a world that weighs the backgrounds they were born into more than their dreams.
When colorful villains come out to play, 8-year-old Zoey has the power to transform into StarBeam, a kid-sized superhero. She saves the day, every day!
Traversing genres, five separate stories offer unique, whimsical and thought-provoking takes on life during the pandemic in 2020.
The theft of the Greater Grail from Fuyuki City leads to a splintered timeline in which the Great Holy Grail War is waged on an unprecedented scale.

Titulo: The Investigator: A British Crime Story
Enredo: After 40 years of inconclusive evidence, renowned criminologist Mark Williams-Thomas re-examines a string of mysterious murders.
They’re guinea pigs! And they’re cars! The fuzzy and adorable molcars have lots of fun adventures in this delightful stop-motion animation.
On the run from the police, an Arizona man crosses into Mexico and gets deeply involved in drug trafficking – with the help of modern technology.
Dreams come true for real families looking for the perfect home tailored to their own unique style, thanks to Shea and Syd McGee of Studio McGee.
Teenage spy McKeyla teams up with three other super-smart girls to become secret agents who use their science and tech skills to save the day.
The popular fashion dolls come to life in this animated series as they let their talents and true colors shine at the visual arts school, Rainbow High.
An art curator's life unravels, as she tries to keep her pastime as a die-hard K-pop fan secret from her gallery's new director.
Curious puppet pals Waffles and Mochi travel the world exploring the wonders of food and culture while learning how to cook with fresh ingredients.
No dog, no breed, no behavior is unfixable for Cali K9's Jas Leverette. Follow the Oakland dog trainer as he works with a range of canines and owners.

Titulo: Nisman: El fiscal, la presidenta y el espía

Enredo: Family man Devin falls back into his sneaker obsession after his pal Bobby talks him into a wheeling-dealing scheme to score a mythical pair of kicks.
High school teens Charley and Ben find themselves in a complicated romance when Ben dies in a tragic accident but is resurrected by a magical spell.
No one can be trusted after a terrorist bombing in Bilbao kills seven and destroys the lives of the suspected jihadi and everyone around him.
Thirty years after a disease that turns the infected into carnivorous insects emerged, a young exterminator and a teenage girl search for her mother.
A penniless country boy goes in search of his runaway sister in Bogotá, where he falls for an aspiring singer, but gets tangled up in organized crime.
Emmy-winning host Bill Nye brings experts and famous guests to his lab for a talk show exploring scientific issues that touch our lives.
Powerful cats, indestructible arachnids and flesh-melting pit vipers are just the beginning in this series about Latin America's deadliest creatures.
Three food and design experts travel the world to revive failing restaurants by connecting them to the local culture beyond their gorgeous views.
An exploration of different personas in an eclectic collection of four works by critically acclaimed Korean directors.
A former high-ranking financial executive finds redemption and romance when he's paroled after a prison sentence and becomes a math teacher.

Titulo: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants
Enredo: Fourth-grade friends George and Harold have a shared love of pranks and comic books – and turning their principal into an undies-wearing superhero.
Determined to bring a Zika vaccine to the remote Pantanal, three doctors clash with a faith healer and are pulled deeper into the mysteries of his cult.
To survive in a dog-eat-dog world, two rival lawyers with high-class clientele tear apart anything that stands in the way of their ambitions.
A tormented student uncovers unsettling secrets at her remote high school as betrayal and a paranormal encounter upend her life.
From secrets and lies to jealousy and control, four stories in this anthology film explore the darker, deceptive sides of love.

Titulo: SAINT SEIYA: Knights of the Zodiac

Enredo: This delightful animated series centers on impish lamb Timmy as he enters nursery school, where he learns about sharing, responsibility and fairness.
Nearly 30 years after her mom's murder, a political strategist launches a calculated plan to ruin the Colombian presidential candidate who killed her.
A stylist, a hair designer and a makeup artist team up to give Britain's biggest fashion disasters some much-needed makeunders.
At Korea's top university medical center, ideals and interests collide between a patient-centered ER doctor and the hospital's newly-appointed CEO.
What happens after we die? This docuseries explores personal stories and research on near-death experiences, reincarnation and paranormal phenomena.
Real life mom-daughter duo Neena and Masaba Gupta play versions of themselves in this playful, fictional peek into their lives in fashion and film.
A couple decides to make their engagement official by honoring tradition when a pandemic forces them and their families to quarantine under one roof.

Titulo: Shaun the Sheep: Adventures from Mossy Bottom
Enredo: Clever sheep Shaun, loyal dog Bitzer and the rest of the Mossy Bottom gang cook up oodles of fun and mischief on the farm.
Frustrated by life with her boyfriend, thirty-something Wako can’t stop herself from being interested in high schooler Yumeaki, despite their age gap.
Miserable and unsuccessful, a woman thinks she's lost all her spark — until one day, her spunky younger self appears in front of her demanding change.

Titulo: Witch Hunt: A Century of Murder
Meet the Drug Lords: Inside the Real Narcos

Enredo: Cute cats, quirky crafts and colorful magic! Join kitty enthusiast Gabby and her sidekick Pandy Paws as they team up for a series of animated adventures.
Reclusive, socially awkward jingle composer Toon must navigate the nightmarish world of show biz after a viral video skyrockets him to fame.
Four individuals at a crossroads in life are given the chance to take both paths, and decide which road is best for them.
Original members of the iconic Monty Python comedy troupe pick their all-time favorite sketches from their groundbreaking television series.
The reality show "WOW!" engages the Winx in their mission, starting an undercover, worldly journey in order to make talented kids' dreams come true.
For six engaged couples, happily ever after begins on a spectacular note in this eye-popping look at India’s multibillion-dollar wedding industry.
Baffling symptoms. Controversial diagnoses. Costly treatments. Seven people with chronic illnesses search for answers – and relief.
Five preteen girls learn they're a legendary superhero squad known as the Glitter Force. Their mission? To defend Earth from evil fairy-tale villains.
On the heels of Junior Rescue training, Team Flounder returns to brave the beach in a series of thrilling saves and lighthearted laughs.
This docuseries profiles unique and dangerous traditional sports from around the world, as well as the communities and cultures where they thrive.
Teen singers-songwriters in an elite music program form bonds of friendship, creativity and romance while turning their passion into their profession.
Take control of an adventure set in the Minecraft universe. The future of the world is at stake, and your decisions shape the story – so choose wisely!
Nobody's safe as Michelle Wolf unapologetically takes aim in this weekly topical show that blends sketches with live comedy and in-studio guests.
With songs made famous by the Beatles, five friendly bugs learn big lessons about the world around them – all from the safety of their own backyard.
In a world where data is no longer private, con artists uncover a sinister surveillance scheme headed by the government and a greedy corporation.
Optimus Prime and the AllSpark are missing – and only a memory-scrambled Bumblebee holds the key to finding them in this animated sci-fi series.
In Dublin, friends Aisling and Danielle must come to terms with adulthood when their millennial hijinks and hangovers begin to wear off.
A young man who's learned nothing about his father from his single mom has a freak accident that sends him back to 1989, the year before he was born.
Lazy, lasagna-loving fat cat Garfield lives life on his own terms, which includes teasing his geeky owner, Jon, and tormenting dimwitted dog Odie.
A big-hearted girl helps her Fuzzly friends who live in her family's hotel with exploring feelings, fixing mishaps and embracing their special quirks.
In feudalistic Lebanon, farmers revolt against the nobility under the leadership of a revolutionary figure who champions the oppressed.
From nature to nurture, this docuseries explores the groundbreaking science that reveals how infants discover life during their very first year.

Titulo: Schulz Saves America: Pandemics, Predators, Protests & Presidents

Enredo: Kumiko and Kenichi meet in college and build a happy marriage together. But over time, an unusual problem threatens to destroy their relationship.
The world's first family is back for more laughs as they discover sports, sleepovers and other wonders in a world of exotic creatures and adventures.
Amid the turmoil of China's civil war, families of Kuomintang pilots face the pain of leaving their homes but find strength in their shared bonds.
In this funny, heartfelt and moving docuseries, real people unpack the fascinating and quirky stories around their most meaningful pieces of clothing.
A new breed of secret agents must stop a ruthless computer virus and its minions from stealing the unlimited clean energy source that created them.
The Masire brothers rule Johannesburg's criminal underworld, but a supernatural family curse and a tangled web of betrayal threaten to destroy them.
In this unscripted series, families passionate about food serve up their most delicious dishes for the chance to be crowned Britain's best home cooks.
When her uptight new boss and landlord starts a war on office romances, plucky Liang-liang quickly starts looking for ways to get him to lighten up.
Sleepless for 24 hours, contestants in the comedy game show stumble through challenges both eccentric and everyday for a chance at a $1 million prize.
Follow the Great White Sharks, a world-champion cheerleading squad, as they juggle the pressures of training, school, work and relationships.
Be yourself or someone else? In this fun reality competition, online players try their best to flirt, bond and catfish their way to a R$300,000 prize.
When the head of the lucrative family business passes away, his will leaves the clan at extreme odds.
After disappearing from the underworld, the legendary yakuza Tatsu, "the Immortal Dragon," resurfaces — as a fiercely devoted stay-at-home husband.
This drama follows Mexican-American singer Jenni Rivera's unlikely rise from suicidal pregnant teen and abused wife to banda superstar.
Young trainer Ash and his new friend Goh become research fellows at Professor Cerise's laboratory, traveling all over the world to learn about Pokémon.
Travel the vast Skylander universe in this animated series as a ragtag group of academy graduates build trust and heart in their fight against evil.
When doubts rise about a five-year-old murder conviction, a veteran detective partners with a young hotshot to hunt down the case's hidden truths.
Comedians Jimmy Carr, D.L. Hughley and Katherine Ryan tackle the world's woes with help from a rotating crew of funny guests and an actual expert.
This fantasy drama follows an indie band singer who repeatedly undergoes unwanted time slips and the girlfriend he must save from an unlucky fate.
With unique individual perspectives that converge into a unified voice, sketch comedy group Astronomy Club delivers a smart and absurd brand of humor.
A prankster prince who wants to experience life as an ordinary teen leaves his kingdom to live incognito with a single mom and her studious son.
A quirk of fate sends an ordinary, sweet-natured high school girl and her father into the home of the school genius, on whom she has a huge crush.
In a place called Numberland, math adds up to tons of fun when a group of cheerful blocks work, play and sing together.
After uncovering a magical locket that allows her to shrink in size, Polly and her friends set out on big adventures with petite power.
Hip-hop icon MC Joe Speed retires from showbiz and finds a new rhythm balancing business, romance and everyday family chaos.
When night falls on the city, shadows and spirits come alive in this horror anthology series centered on urban legends.
Happy-go-lucky chicken Archibald may not remember to do his chores, but he never forgets to have fun. After all, life's an adventure!
A programming genius builds a fact-finding, truth-seeking internet portal while reckoning with trouble at home.
Julien's been dethroned, but loyal friends and some very unlikely allies will propel the lovable lemur on a colorful journey to take back his kingdom.
Twins Dak and Leyla and their dragon friends devote their lives to rescuing others, defending their home of Huttsgalor and having fun along the way.
Players and coaches for a Montreal soccer team chase dreams of stardom while their personal lives erupt with love, fear, passion and violence.
In this reality show, couples overcome obstacles to celebrate their love in surprise dream weddings designed by three experts in less than a week.
Seeking a greater justice, a band of homeless assassins flays their human targets and delivers the tattooed skins as proof of a contract fulfilled.
When things don't go her way during a shooting for her new show, a top actress runs away in an old van that guides her on a time-traveling journey.
Ya-nuo's been raised as a boy. Now at age 25, she's caught the eye of a triad leader's sister. But what happens when she reveals her true gender?
Meet eccentric homeowners whose seemingly ordinary spaces are full of surprises, from a backyard roller coaster to an indoor aquarium.
From fangs to claws to venomous stings, they all wield deadly weapons. But which creature will be crowned the fiercest of all?
A mysterious gift from her late parents sends 12-year-old Mia into an enchanted world of elves, unicorns and an evil queen named Panthea.
A tough young man with a short temper and no patience for bullies gains a legendary reputation as the best street fighter in Busan.

Titulo: The Unknown Hitman: The Story of El Cholo Adrián

Enredo: In this reality series, a tight-knit group of Deaf and hard of hearing students share their stories and explore life at Gallaudet University.
An honest lawyer reaches a moral crossroads after the cops force her to inform on her incarcerated brother, the leader of a rising criminal faction.
A teen gamer is forced to level up to full-time babysitter when his favorite video game drops three superpowered infants from space into his backyard.
Young koala caretaker Izzy Bee and her family rescue cuddly creatures in need and help them head back into the wild on Australia’s Magnetic Island.
When something's wrong in the Rainbow Kingdom, bighearted guardian True and her best friend, Bartleby, are there to grant wishes and save the day.
A new generation of teen heroes uses superhuman ninja powers to battle the intergalactic villain Galvanax and save Earth from destruction.

Titulo: LEGO Jurassic World: Legend of Isla Nublar
Enredo: At Jurassic Park, a velociraptor handler and an operations manager tackle crises of epic proportions as they try to prevent dinosaur-sized disasters.
When her fugitive husband leaves her homeless and penniless, a once-wealthy woman has no other choice but to join the working class.
A pair of high-powered, successful lawyers find themselves defending opposite interests of the justice system, causing a strain on their happy marriage.
It's everything you love about "Sugar Rush" – with a holly jolly holiday twist – in this Christmas-themed spin on competitive baking.
Follow the outrageous, high-octane adventures of Buddy Thunderstruck, a truck-racing dog who brings guts and good times to the town of Greasepit.
Explore the psychological machinations and immoral behavior that define the most nefarious types of criminals.
A Christmas reunion becomes a gateway to the past in this three-part series that explores the intimate complexities of one family's history.
"Roastmaster General" Jeff Ross and a slew of guest stars poke fun at major historical figures while also honoring their enduring impact on the world.
Reggie's wild imagination unlocks a weird and wonderful world where she can be herself – and escape the pressures of growing up.
Wielding a light-up sword through the dark corners of a high school, a nurse with an unusual gift protects students from monsters only she can see.
A dramatic series about friendship and conflict between two comedians who search for meaning in life and comedy. Based on the prize-winning book.
Hoping to make a comeback after a bad scandal, an actress agrees to research a new role by taking a job as a secretary for a prickly attorney.
Follow Indian Premier League champions Mumbai Indians through the 2018 season in this series featuring insider insights and intense cricket action.
The history of military tanks unfolds in a documentary series that traces their role in history and geopolitics from World War I to the 21st century.
Decadent pasta from day-old fries? Skillful cooks transform tired leftovers into tantalizing new dishes in this wildly creative culinary competition.
Fun-loving friends Daisy and Cole use music and imagination to solve problems in a town filled with nursery rhyme characters.
Handy and inventive pup Tag chases adventure with her best pal, Scooch, solving problems and helping the citizens of Pawston along the way.
A child star in the '80s, Samantha clings to the fringes of celebrity with hilarious harebrained schemes to launch herself back into the spotlight.
In a town filled with food, Bread is a master cake decorator who gives life-changing makeovers that will put any customer in an amazing mood.
An innocent toddler’s boundless curiosity – and extraordinary might – lead to mischief and adventure in his small Indian town.
To his family's frustration, Henry is skilled at making trouble, from babysitting pets in his bedroom to starting a shark panic at the swimming pool.
Two quirky cats, Ollie and Moon, and their friend Stanley the snail travel the world, solving everyday problems and learning about different cultures.
Half dinosaur, half construction truck, full-on fun! Watch giant Ty Rux, his little buddy Revvit and the crew come face-to-face with evil D-Structs.

Titulo: Close Your Eyes Before It's Dark

Enredo: A 14-year-old takes ownership of a toy company and hires a group of his friends to help him create amazing new toys.
After training with legendary Valt Aoi, Dante and his trusty Ace Dragon lead the next generation of Bladers to battle in Japan — Beyblade's birthplace.
When Earth's animals and natural wonders need a rescue, the Rainbow Rangers combine their colorful powers to protect the planet and save the day!
As four Russian friends grow up in the early '60s, life, love and the curse of success threaten to derail their dreams.
Beautiful executive assistant Zeina reluctantly teams up with the self-assured Tarek to chase down an elusive dollar bill worth $1 million.
Take an intimate look at the emotionally charged first and last days of new and soon-to-be released inmates at Georgia's Gwinnett County Jail.
Down-and-out musician Bastian battles the blues as he returns home for Christmas and encounters a series of not-so-cheery surprises.
Suddenly a widow, a woman rekindles her thirst for life by becoming a eulogist while navigating the existential landscape of death, grief and love.
This miniseries spinoff of "Rita" follows teacher Hjørdis as she plans a school play on bullying featuring a cast of socially awkward students.
When a girl vanishes from a suburb near Mexico City, the personal goals of some involved in the case muddy the search. Based on a true story.
In this reality series, the bickering but big-hearted Bernards manage their budget-friendly funeral home while helping grieving families say farewell.
Two gutsy food delivery workers strive to overcome their socioeconomic disadvantages to achieve big goals – and bump into love along the way.

Titulo: Kevin Hart: Don't F**k This Up

Enredo: After going to a Halloween party, college student Luis Andrés Colmenares is found dead. Was it an accident or murder? Inspired by true events.
Top Hollywood stars and directors open up about their dreams, struggles and lifelong obsessions in interviews filmed in front of a live audience.
Host Chris Packham examines bizarre natural phenomena from around the globe, from strange creatures to geographical oddities.
Full of funny one-liners and always ready for an adventure, a talking cat and his equally chatty animal cohorts set out to become famous.
A talented singer falls in love at first sight with a music prodigy who has an affinity for lies – and a knack for being a hit-making producer.
Fueled by his own rough upbringing, Snoop Dogg creates a youth football league to keep at-risk kids off the streets and focused on their goals.
Science-loving host Emily Calandrelli makes STEAM fun with activities, demonstrations and at-home experiments that'll make you think — and blow your mind!
In 1890s Malacca, Li Lan finds herself in the afterlife and becomes mired in a mystery linked to the sinister, deceased son of a wealthy family.
West Coast Customs, a mecca for well-heeled car lovers, stars as their team creates some of the most luxurious, outrageous vehicles on the planet.
As a chief of staff in the National Assembly, Jang Tae-jun influences power behind the scenes while pursuing his own ambitions to rise to the top.
Furry friends take a re-bark-able journey in this series about an extraordinary school for the cutest, cuddliest and most curious puppies.
Four sisters deal with family drama and secrets throughout three different time periods, all occurring on Christmas Day.
Acclaimed filmmakers from around the world channel their creativity during COVID-19 isolation with this diverse, genre-spanning collection of short films.
After scientists discover a mysterious substance that can influence human minds, two factions wage an all-out battle to control its awesome power.
This true crime series shows how innocent people have been convicted with dubious forensic techniques and tools such as touch DNA and cadaver dogs.

Titulo: Apache: La vida de Carlos Tevez

Enredo: A misfit alien named Oh moves in with Tip and her family, in a series that picks up the dynamic duo's adventures where the hit film left off.
With her dad away, Mavis is so ready for adventure – if strict Aunt Lydia doesn't stop her first. Set four years before the "Hotel Transylvania" film.

Titulo: A Little Help with Carol Burnett
Enredo: Comedy icon Carol Burnett returns to TV with a panel of clever kids, who help adults and celebrity guests solve their problems with brutal honesty.
Adorable puppets stage their own musical under the watchful eye of mentor Julie Andrews in this original kids' series from the Jim Henson Company.
Get to know Barbie and her BFFs – including next-door neighbor Ken – in this animated vlog of adventures filmed inside her family's new dreamhouse.
While investigating an actress’s supposed suicide and her connection to the mafia, a veteran journalist discovers that corruption runs deep.
A refined young Joseon scholar's life turns upside down after he rescues a drunk princess who later accuses him of taking something precious from her.
A boy suddenly orphaned fights his parents' killer to save a planet, and discovers a new world of danger — and wonder.
Stranded on a tropical island, two silly larva buddies find slapstick fun in everything from discovering food to meeting new animal friends.
Paw-esome tales abound when singing furry friends Lampo, Milady, Pilou and Meatball band together.
Ten years after a once-promising student graduates, she finds herself working at a cosmetics company run by the boy with the worst grades in school.
Over the course of a fishing season, tough men and women pursue lucrative albacore tuna in the competitive waters off the Oregon coast.
In this docuseries, soccer great Diego Maradona comes to Culiacán, the heart of the Sinaloa Cartel, to save the local team, the Dorados, and maybe himself, too.
Get up close and personal with avalanches, fiery volcanoes and other natural cataclysms, and learn why some choose to live in their destructive paths.
Four intrepid and impulsive police officers form a special narcotics unit to combat the birth of drug trafficking on Spain's Costa del Sol in the 1970s.
Join Turbo and his posse, the Fast Action Stunt Team. Filled with comedy, action and fun, this series amps it up to the extreme.

Titulo: The Forest of Love: Deep Cut
Enredo: Nothing's as it seems when a charismatic conman and an aspiring film crew delve into the lives of two emotionally scarred women.
Falsely incriminated, Abla Fahita is separated from her kids, but the self-indulgent diva will stop at nothing to redeem herself and reunite her family.
When an evil force threatens his village, a gifted teen who can talk to ghosts puts his skills to good use, one legend at a time.
A love letter to pork belly — a perennial favorite among Koreans of every generation — unfolds with an exploration of its history and cooking methods.
Bad tattoos walk in. Great tattoos walk out. Top artists transform tattoo disasters into stunning cover-ups, with designs chosen by clients' loved ones.
Aided by tablets found near a downed meteorite, Max, Rex and Zoe race the evil Alpha Gang as they travel the globe in search of living dinosaurs.

Titulo: Once Upon a Time in Lingjian Mountain

Enredo: These uncanny tales reveal a world where individuals face the tragic consequences of social pressure, parental oppression and family dysfunction.

Titulo: The Prince Who Turns into a Frog
Enredo: Before his wedding, a cold CEO is hit by a car and awakens a changed man. As he and the driver fall in love, more changes appear on the road ahead.
Bickering siblings Shi Miao and Shi Fen tackle friendship matters, school drama and the pitfalls of growing up with little parental supervision.
Despite their estranged families, Juman and Hisham fall in love and get married but their different outlooks on life soon threaten their relationship.
Young lyricists between the ages of 12 and 16 compete for a chance to sign to Jermaine Dupri's label while being mentored by hip-hop and R&B's finest.
Follow the Chinle High basketball team in Arizona's Navajo Nation on a quest to win a state championship and bring pride to their isolated community.
Beep, beep – go, go! Buckle up for fun and adventure with adorable kid car Cory Carson as he explores the winding roads of Bumperton Hills.
Classic nursery rhymes and children's songs get a fresh twist in this high-energy program that helps kids learn as they dance and sing along.
Hand-picked by Tiffany Haddish, six diverse comedians showcase their raw humor in a series of specials oozing with energy.
A reluctant clairvoyant joins forces with a brusque police detective hiding a soft heart to help him solve criminal cases using her psychic abilities.
After losing his sight and his fiancee in an accident, a man hires a caregiver who mysteriously sounds – and looks – just like his late girlfriend.
A spinoff of Rohit Shetty's action franchise, this animated series follows brave kid cop Little Singham’s adventures as he defends his town from evil.
Preschool kids whose parents are the world's most famous monsters try to master their special powers while preparing for kindergarten.

Titulo: How to Ruin Christmas: The Wedding

Enredo: Three engineering students deal with dorm drama, date around, and do whatever it takes to make their dreams come true.
TV star David Hasselhoff hopes to reboot his career in the U.K., but both his comeback plans and his personal life keep going off the rails.

Titulo: Larry Charles' Dangerous World of Comedy
Enredo: Legendary comedy writer and director Larry Charles travels the world in search of humor in the most unusual, unexpected and dangerous places.
After jostling her way into a gig as a celebrity bodyguard, the boisterous daughter of a powerful triad boss shakes up a TV star's life and finds love.

Titulo: Get Organized with The Home Edit
Enredo: Expert home organizers Clea and Joanna help celebrities and everyday clients edit, categorize and contain their clutter to create stunning spaces.
A young journalist is forced into a life of crime to save his father and family in this series based on the novel by Miguel Sáez Carral.
Filmed in isolation, this narrative anthology series features both dark and funny takes on how people strive to stay connected while staying apart.
When an aspiring actress hits it big thanks to a candid Instagram post, the lives of several Tokyo women cross as they struggle to define happiness IRL.
Cast members, writers, producers and mental health professionals discuss some of the difficult issues and themes explored in "13 Reasons Why."

Titulo: One on One with Kirk Cameron

Enredo: A wedding planner and a real estate agent compete to win the hearts and budgets of spouses-to-be. Will they pick fairy-tale nuptials or a dream home?
An enterprising cupcake and his cheerful dinosaur brother take on jobs of all sorts as they work to help friends and strangers in their eccentric city.
The Ice Tribe prince journeys to a sacred mountain to vanquish evil but soon finds himself at war with the Fire Tribe, led by his long-lost brother.
A third-generation chaebol falls in love with a woman who opens his eyes to the struggles of the working class and inspires him to make a difference.
This reality series follows the lives of a group of wealthy, successful Latina women in Los Angeles.
Furry little bunnies hop through wild adventures as they find solutions, fun and sometimes mischief wherever there is light.
Jake Armstrong and his best friends are unexpectedly transformed into superheroes who learn to reach far beyond the limits of any ordinary teenager.
Fresh voices bring some of the most famous names in history to life. A live-action sketch comedy show based on the series of best-selling books.
Former bride and forever comedian Jamie Lee shares her irreverent yet practical tips and tricks for wedding planning with struggling lovebirds.
Plucky lizard Oscar spends his time trying to avoid the hazards of the desert, including marauding chickens and bumbling adversaries.
With his vivid imagination, Simon the rabbit searches for fun while learning about the importance of responsibility and communication.
This series examines the nature of cuteness and how adorability helps some animal species to survive and thrive in a variety of environments.
In the interview room, detectives go head-to-head with suspects and try to get to the truth – even if it means breaking the rules and risking it all.
Four girls summon their inner superheroes to defend Earth and the magical kingdom of Splendorius from King Mercenare and his minions.
Nine struggling musicians share the spotlight in this deeply personal reality series about the challenges and thrills of staging a Hollywood showcase.
Alien reporters Ixbee, Pixbee and Squee travel to a lovely but odd planet called Earth, where they attempt to make sense of humans and their hobbies.
Everything changes for talented young gymnast Jenny Cortez when she moves with her family from Miami to Toronto to open a new gymnastics club.
This anthology follows 12 different love stories involving fateful encounters, magical moments and unexpected romances over the course of a year.
With exciting trips to the big city, the ski slopes and beyond, the Veggie friends expand their horizons and learn valuable faith-based lessons.
A college stud tries to level up his relationship with a computer science major after becoming attracted to her skills in an online role-playing game.
Two mischievous yet lovable five-year-old twins and their friends enjoy daily life and new discoveries with the residents of their Malaysian village.
Follow the reporters at BuzzFeed as they probe topics ranging from quirky internet crazes to safe injection spaces for opioid users.
A former footballer tries to make it as a player agent in the world of African soccer, but a secret from his past threatens to destroy everything.

Titulo: Garth Brooks: The Road I'm On

Enredo: Eight undocumented families' fates roller-coast as the United States' immigration policies are transformed.
The letters of the alphabet come to life in Alphaland as they read, write and spell their way into an exciting world of phonic fun.
A determined woman works to rid an Argentine soccer club of the violent crime and corruption surrounding its intense fanbase.

Titulo: The Witcher: A Look Inside the Episodes
Enredo: With series creator Lauren S. Hissrich as your guide, take an in-depth journey into the stories and themes powering the first season of "The Witcher."
Trained dancer Vandana Hart travels the world to learn traditional and urban dance styles from the local experts who know them best.
A city kid is brought to the countryside by his father's new coaching gig: reviving a ragtag middle school badminton team on the brink of extinction.
In this faith-based docuseries, Bishop Ezekiel Williams builds an inspiring, nontraditional gospel choir with the help of superstar nephew Pharrell.
A plucky young orphan sent to live with her grandfather in the mountains discovers wonder and adventure around every corner.
A jaded rom-com screenwriter in her 30s mines four love-sick women for their stories under the guise of providing them with romantic advice.
On a quest to reunite with her trusty rider, a fearless war horse journeys through a whimsical world filled with magic, adventure and singing centaurs.
Through intense prison interviews, Piers Morgan revisits the crimes of three convicted serial killers and learns more about their motives.
In this new take on a classic tale, an ancient snake spirit transforms into a beautiful woman and falls in love with a doctor unaware of her true form.
Follow talent management company Pets on Q as they work with the biggest animal influencers on social media in this reality series.
Delightful cakes and heavenly breads pop from the oven as Nadiya Hussain returns to baking, her happy place, and spotlights creative kindred spirits.
Skeptics and others discuss widely held conspiracy theories involving aliens, government cover-ups, secret assassinations and other intrigues.
Magician Drummond Money-Coutts travels the globe, sharing his infectious love of his craft and attempting feats that proved fatal to other magicians.
When an evicted single mom's estranged father dies, she and his second wife cover up his death after learning they've been written out of his will.
Ride along as police officers and drug smugglers go toe-to-toe, trying to outwit each other in locales around the world.
Imaginative boy Ben transforms his city by bringing colorful street art to life, armed with a magic paintbrush – and the classic sounds of Motown.
Featuring the boys of Johnny's West, a gang of zany transfer students are recruited for a mysterious mission ordained by their shadowy principal.
Sebastián is a radio show host of modest fame, trying to find a way in the world as he deals with his ex-wife (whom he still loves) and two kids.
Four friends become guardians of the island Gorm and must harness powers of the elements to stop an evil lord and his army from ruling the kingdom.
A Brooklyn youth football program and its selfless coaches provide a safe haven for kids to compete and learn lessons that will take them far in life.
In Jeddah, Saudi Arabia, a young aspiring filmmaker and his circle of friends grapple with family expectations, gender roles, romance and rivalry.
Actor Jaaved Jaafferi brings his signature humor to this Hindi dubbing of the show where teams creatively navigate rooms flooded with make-believe lava.
Fading music biz veteran Zé realizes he has just one more chance at redemption: He must assemble a hit boy band from a ragtag group of pop newbies.
Māori funeral directors Francis and Kaiora Tipene and staff temper good humor with care and respect as they help Polynesian families cope with loss.
At their high school, a group of unruly teens wreak havoc, face bullies and navigate turbulent lives beyond school grounds.
A group of teens get caught up in a supernatural clash as vengeful spirits from centuries past rise up in the Liberdade district of São Paulo.
Life is ever-delightful — and ever-challenging — for a group of friends in their twilight years as they rediscover themselves through love and family.
Two astronauts attempt to brave a life in Earth's orbit on a record-setting mission to see if humans have the endurance to survive a flight to Mars.
An egotistic top male model and a pretty model wannabe are forced to live each other's lives until they figure out a way to undo their body switch.
Years after taking up normal lives incognito, the cyborgs are forced to fight again when the superhuman Blessed appear with a plan for humanity.

Titulo: Dave Chappelle: Equanimity & The Bird Revelation
Enredo: Comedy titan Dave Chappelle caps a wild year with two stand-up specials packed with scorching new material, self-reflection and tough love.

Titulo: Check The Store Next Door: The Next Chapter
Enredo: When a former shop owner grows bored of retirement, he buys a fish pond and manages the new hijinks in his life with a staff of quirky employees.
A language major bickers with – and falls for – a doctoral student as she navigates the ups and downs of love and friendship with college classmates.
As they learn their routes around the busy city, Tayo and his little bus friends discover new sights and go on exciting adventures every day.
Spirited sister-brother duo Cleo and Cuquín try on different professions each day to help their other siblings solve problems and enjoy new adventures.
Inspector Gadget is back and must face his old enemy, the evil Dr. Claw, who has reactivated MAD, his global crime syndicate.
A med student with a supernatural gift tries to cash in on his abilities by facing off against ghosts, till a wandering spirit brings romance instead.
In this Spanish adaptation of "Magic for Humans," folks of all ages on the streets of Barcelona are amazed by tricks that inspire delight and wonder.
After surviving a near-fatal injury on the job, a cop sets out to investigate a conspiracy involving the top brass of the police department.
Comedian Ryuji Akiyama satirizes top “creators” in Japan with a deadpan, unerring eye for humor, with help from some surprising celebrity guest stars.
A diverse group of up-and-coming comedians perform 15-minute sets in this stand-up comedy showcase series.
New beginnings or old baggage? Four singles have one chance to reignite romance with an ex – or leave the past behind for good.
Charlie creates fun stories using different shapes, and he needs your help! Take off for adventures in outer space, the Wild West – and right at home.

Titulo: Cloudy with a Chance of Meatballs
Enredo: When inventor Flint Lockwood makes clouds rain food, the citizens of Chewandswallow can feed themselves. But a bowl of disaster is about to overflow.
After a brush with the law, teen celebrity Kaylie Konrad swaps social stardom for court-ordered chaos as a middle school wilderness club leader.
A cast of quirky critters and Mother Nature herself narrate this funny science series, which peeks into the lives of Earth’s most incredible animals.
Catch a ride with the Mighty Express — a team of trains and their kid friends who overcome trouble on the tracks with quick thinking and teamwork!
Amid crime and corruption, the lives of two couples intertwine as unexpected events soon reveal their dark secrets and tainted pasts.
Two nefarious schemes taking place 10 years apart entangle a dauntless triad member, who must break out of prison to rescue a loved one.
A department store mogul has his son work incognito in a menial job to prove his worthiness, while female co-workers teach him how normal people live.

Titulo: Club de Cuervos Presents: The Ballad of Hugo Sánchez
Enredo: Chava Iglesias's doting personal assistant Hugo Sánchez is tasked with leading Club de Cuervos to victory in Nicaragua – if only his mom will let him.
There's an organization gathering espers for a nefarious purpose. Powerful psychic Mob, however, is just trying to be the protagonist of his own life.
A coldhearted heiress, a man from her past and an ambitious new hire in her company all become entangled on a battleground for money and power.

Titulo: Lego Bionicle: The Journey to One

Enredo: From the mind of comedian Iliza Shlesinger comes a fun, irreverent mix of kooky characters, sly social commentary and pop culture gags.
This series looks at the stories behind the athletes and countries that have achieved World Cup champion status.
Dan Kouzo and his pals bond with mysterious creatures known as Bakugan while fighting sinister forces out to control the world.
Law enforcement officials look back on attempted terrorist attacks that were thwarted in the nick of time.
When accused of a murder eerily parallel to a plot in his novel, a best-selling crime writer must navigate a web of hidden enemies.
Keeping peace and safety in Train World is no easy task, but for five trains with the power to transform into robots, every crisis is an adventure!
A complicated, one-sided secret attraction sends ripples through the lives of a mild-mannered student and her dashing classmate.
Beautiful housewife Xie An Zhen seems to be living the perfect life but finds her world crumbling after learning that her husband is cheating on her.
Little animals embark on big adventures across the U.S. in a dramatic nature series that explores their hidden worlds and epic survival stories.

Titulo: A Taiwanese Tale of Two Cities
Enredo: A Taipei doctor and a San Francisco engineer swap homes in a daring pact, embarking on journeys filled with trials, secrets and unexpected encounters.
Shocking secrets begin to unravel when the aftermath of a car crash leaves four best friends questioning the truth of their relationships.

Titulo: Standup and Away! with Brian Regan

Enredo: This drama portrays women and kids living under the Islamic State group: a Yazidi slave, an undercover reporter, a recruited mom and child snipers.
Seven men and women board a pink bus in search of true love. On a journey through Asia with strangers, their goal is to return to Japan as a couple.
It's drama Down Under when expectant mothers with model good looks and lavish lifestyles pull out all the stops to prepare for their new arrivals.
A troubled psychologist returns from the U.S. and sets up a clinic in Taiwan, where mysterious patients and uncanny events shed light on his murky past.
As the owner of a group of international schools, a man gets caught in a series of scams as his wife, a principal, rules his life with an iron fist.
Discover the brilliant dancers and choreographers who are shaping the art of movement around the world in this documentary series.
The competition is fierce — and the drama undeniable — as a group of young and hungry agents try to seal the deal on luxury listings in the Hamptons.
Love blooms between a bubbly, aspiring voice actress and a cool, enigmatic violin-maker after they cross paths on a reality TV show.

Titulo: Littlest Pet Shop: A World of Our Own
Enredo: In Paw-Tucket, pets of all types form friendships, pursue their passions and have a great time being themselves.
In this animated spinoff series, Juni and Carmen Cortez must battle the evil organization S.W.A.M.P. – without the help of their super-spy parents.
A stone's throw from Africa, the Spanish beach town of La Línea is a drug smuggling hot spot. But the police and mayor are determined to change that.
When she gets angry, middle schooler Naoko turns into fierce dinosaur Gauko! Thanks to friends, aliens and more, her life is full of wacky incidents.
A timid, small-town comedian's long-awaited big break takes a dark turn when he realizes committing murder is the only way to keep his onstage mojo.
Wen Nuan signs on to work as the executive assistant to ex Zhan Nanxian at his tech firm. Helping him at work just may lead her back into his heart.
When a mysterious box arrives at his door, a doctor and father is forced to participate in a twisted killing game, or risk losing everything.
This global stand-up comedy series features a diverse set of comics from 13 regions bringing their perspectives on what's funny around the world.
A near-death experience spurs a feared drug lord to leave behind his life of crime and infidelity, to the disbelief of everyone close to him.
Six hopeful friends journey into adulthood to create the moments that pull them together, draw them apart and make them fall in love.
From allergies to diet to sleep, three friendly doctors share expert advice, bust medical myths and test the latest treatments.
Four of Colombia's funniest and bawdiest comedians perform before a post-quarantine audience hungry for their stories.
When disaster strikes in Brooms Town, police car Robocar Poli, fire truck Robotruck Roy and their friends on the rescue team race to save the day.
Ruby makes magical journeys with her teddy bear Choco to Rainbow Village, where her toys come to life – and where there's always a problem to solve!
In Justin's dreams, he and his imaginary friends Olive and Squidgy travel around the world learning about nature and other cultures.
A domestic abuse survivor orchestrates an elaborate deception to protect her family from her powerfully wealthy husband and his vindictive enemies.
In this fun, fast-paced music contest hosted by Tituss Burgess, players sing their hearts out and try to hit the right notes to win up to $60,000.
Harrowing and hilarious tests await the brave and foolhardy, as well as the judges, in this comedy game show. If they flinch, they feel the pain.
Two curious worms spend their days investigating the otherworldly objects that fall through the grate into their subterranean world.
Step into the cutthroat world of kids' ballroom dancing, where ambitious instructors, proud parents and pint-sized performers waltz to win.
Characters from the popular StoryBots apps for early childhood education give musical lessons on math, science, history, behaviors, emotions and more.
A broken spaceship strands four very tiny aliens on Earth, where they discover an adventure (and strange dangers!) that they never expected.

Titulo: LEGO Jurassic World: The Secret Exhibit

Enredo: Gabrielle Reece hosts a transformative competition of tough fitness challenges as 10 women partner with 10 elite personal trainers.
When mythical creatures come to life, it's up to Leo, Teodora, Don Andrés and Alebrije – super-secret monster hunters – to save the day.
With winter behind them, Bheem and his townspeople usher in a sunny new season in all their favorite ways during the Makar Sankranti festival.
Join host Jeff Foxworthy as contestants test their knowledge of all things biblical, competing to win money for the charities of their choice.
After losing her family in a suspicious car crash, a woman awakens from a 13-year coma determined to expose the truth about the long-ago tragedy.

Titulo: GAME ON: A Comedy Crossover Event
Enredo: Worlds collide in this special event featuring familiar faces, surprise cameos and stories of spirited competition from four different comedy series.
In the midst of a field exercise operating I-Machines, Alliance Academy student Maya Mikuri is thrown into an entirely different kind of adventure.
When a prominent politician is murdered, the intrepid journalists of Frente Tijuana risk their lives to uncover the truth.
This animated series follows young Mowgli and his animal mentors Bagheera and Baloo, who do their best to protect him from fierce tiger Shere Khan.
Heartbroken and romantically pessimistic, a commercial director meets a young artist and teaches him life-changing lessons about love.
Skin and beauty expert Nurse Jamie and plastic surgeon Dr. Sheila Nazarian use the latest procedures to bring out their clients' best selves.
Love snackable, snap-worthy songs? Sing along with the Rhyme Time Town friends as they use their imaginations and flex their problem-solving skills!
Race along with Ricky Zoom and his loyal Bike Buddies as they zip around their two-wheeled town of Wheelford on rescue missions and learn speedy stunts!
The adorable Best Popple Pals love helping their friends and neighbors, but every time they do it seems to backfire in hilarious ways.

Titulo: Edgar Rice Burroughs' Tarzan and Jane
Enredo: Saved from a plane crash and given supernatural powers, teen Tarzan joins forces with brave city girl Jane to protect his jungle home from threats.

Titulo: Chico Bon Bon: Monkey with a Tool Belt
Enredo: Armed with tools and engineering smarts, monkey mechanic Chico Bon Bon and his Fix-It Force help the people of Blunderburg solve all of their problems.
Betrothed while in utero, a resort group president enters into an arranged marriage with a legal assistant. Despite their bickering, love blooms.
After getting dropped from an elite program, a student gets tangled in the affairs of a high school gang while trying to find her own identity.
Players, fans and staff of soccer powerhouse Boca Juniors provide an exclusive, behind-the-scenes look at Argentina's legendary club.

Titulo: Holiday Home Makeover with Mr. Christmas
Enredo: Interior designer Benjamin “Mr. Christmas” Bradley works with a trusty team of "elves” to help families transform their homes for the holidays.
The fun, fondant and hilarious cake fails head to Mexico, where very amateur bakers compete to re-create elaborate sweet treats for a cash prize.

Titulo: Cabins in the Wild with Dick Strawbridge
Enredo: Engineer Dick Strawbridge and craftsman Will Hardie tour eight unique cabins built for a pop-up hotel in Wales, and construct No. 9 on their own.
Teenage friends plan an epic trip to Comic-Con to meet their idol, only to get caught in one hilariously awkward predicament after another.
In 1970s Melbourne, a DJ named Boori Monty Pryor and his brother Paul navigate racial tensions and police encounters amid disco and discrimination.
A university lecturer in Russia returns to Egypt after her husband's sudden disappearance, uncovering further mysteries the more she investigates.

Titulo: I'm with the Band: Nasty Cherry
Enredo: In an unfiltered, intimate docuseries, pop star mentor Charli XCX finds out what it takes to build – and break – a real, badass all-girl punk band.
Pinky Malinky sees the bright side of everything, including being born a hot dog. With his BFFs in tow, this little wiener takes a bite out of life.
The peaceful lives of the residents inhabiting a breathtaking seaside town are shaken following a series of macabre crimes.
An Egyptian doctor becomes a police informant and uses his rare gift of tracking ancient artifacts in the smuggling business.
A determined Qing dynasty princess contends with palace intrigue and a vendetta against her family while navigating the treacherous terrain of romance.
An engaged couple travels the world for a year to explore marriage customs in diverse cultures. Will the journey bring them closer or tear them apart?
Four best friends and spirited career women navigate the treacherous world of romance – even as it stands in the way of work and friendship.
When a sudden death brings everyone’s dirty secrets to the surface, the lives and marriages of a group of close-knit friends unravel out of control.
A young woman's life gets a jump-start after she and a musical genius are both struck by the same falling star. But will the side effects derail love?
Polar opposites in personality and looks, fraternal twin sisters who live completely different lives wake up one day to find they've switched bodies.
She swore not to meddle in her kids' lives like her mother-in-law meddled in hers. But when her sons get married, that vow proves not so easy to keep.
The intimate lives of young men and women from Hong Kong are linked by loosely connected stories about love, lust, separation and deceit.
Two parallel life paths begin for a man and woman in love after she is offered a lucrative promotion far away and must choose between love and career.
Interviews with scholars and dramatic reenactments bring to life the origins and history-making achievements of the world's greatest ancient empires.
Megastar Jay Chou joins his A-list friends in this globe-trotting variety show packed with music and magic tricks.
The extraordinary life and career of flamenco legend Camarón de la Isla is covered in this sweeping biography series.
In 2050, an evil scientist is about to unleash an army of robotic dinosaurs. Now it's up to Kong and friends to fight back and save the day.
As California's 2016 fire season rages, brave backcountry firefighters race to put out the flames, protect homes and save lives in this docuseries.
Meet Bailey, Franny, Kip and Lulu. They're adorable baby animals, and they want you to join the party and help them learn!
A kid transforms into an action figure-sized superhero and teams with his toys in a fight against a villainous robot to save the world.
A baker by day and demon fighter by night, a reincarnated deity must jog his amnesiac lover's memory of their millennium-long romance.
A trio of delinquent brothers fends off neighborhood rivals until one joins a gang to gain protection for the upper-class girl he loves.
Losing her memory – and her boyfriend – after a car accident, Jia-en crosses paths with a heart transplant recipient who helps her recall her past.
A night market vendor clashes with a lofty celebrity chef in a culinary challenge, fueling the first sparks of a romance.
On this fun and funny competition show, home bakers talented in catastrophe struggle to re-create dessert masterpieces and win a 5,000 euro prize.
A wealthy heir's search for a nameless childhood sweetheart leads him to an inn run by a family with three sisters. But which one is his true love?
The BattlBox crew tests out products designed to help people survive dangerous situations, including explosions, natural disasters and intruders.
On a visit to his hometown, a rich bachelor seeks revenge on the woman who broke his heart 10 years ago. But his plan doesn't go as expected.
A quirky fashion student becomes the nanny of a handsome widower’s three kids, experiencing a series of silly antics and schemes.
This docuseries delves into the untold stories and unsung heroes that paved Nigeria's road to independence. Based on the books by host Olasupo Shasore.
An orphaned Chinese woman in Singapore refuses to yield to her lowly station in life, setting her family on a tumultuous course for generations.
After turning his veggies into green energy, Richie Rich earns a trillion dollars overnight and a new life filled with nonstop fun and adventure.
A U.S. Marshal arrives at a small town in Nevada, only to learn that his preacher brother is dead after standing up to the town's mayor and outlaws.
In Lagos, Nigeria, four successful women on the verge of 50 take stock of their lives and loves over the course of one week.
Fairy tales get a funny twist when Masha retells them, because she tends to get the details just a little jumbled up in this animated kids' series.
Despite their fathers' rivalry, two university students form a friendship at a boxing gym as they tackle family drama, romance and personal crises.
Equipped with crayons and his creativity, a boy with autism draws an imaginary world where his animal pals help him tackle real-life situations.

Titulo: What She Put on the Table
Enredo: Based on the life of TV chef Fu Pei-mei, this drama follows two women – one rich, the other poor – who fortuitously cross paths in 1950s Taiwan.
A hardworking man in a thankless job meets a mysterious doctor who sells him powerful pills that throw his life into disarray.
In South London, tradition clashes with culture as a Nigerian father tries to instill his old-fashioned African values into his modern British family.
An inseparable couple struggles to stay together when betrayal threatens to tear their lives apart.
In this animated action series, a rookie driver seeks glory in a world-class auto race, but he’ll need more than just his talent behind the wheel.
An online matchmaker who's convinced she's living under a curse finds her theories on life and love tested when she meets a shrewd divorce expert.
After ditching her domestic life to become a chef, a clueless maid crosses paths with two charming suitors who help her reach her dreams.

Titulo: LEGO Friends: The Power of Friendship
Enredo: Five best friends face adventures side by side in their hometown. Zany antics, love and missteps are better with friends!
To carry out her dad's wish and discover her roots, Dai Tian-qing embarks on a journey around Taiwan and finds love and redemption on the way.
In 1940 Argentina, a Jewish 17-year-old on vacation with her family falls in love with a young Nazi lawyer staying at the same hotel.
An inept magician pulls off the trick of his life: accidentally disappearing a wanted criminal during a police raid. Now he's going to pay for that.
Two live performances, one in English and one in Spanish. No matter the language, Felipe Esparza is muy muy.
True and her friends are dropping sweet, silly beats with freshly modern music videos set to the sounds of classic nursery rhyme songs.
After a traumatic incident at a party makes her a target of gossip and derision, a young college student tries to change her school's toxic culture.
After the death of a loved one, a woman decides to pursue her passion for writing by penning television scripts.

Titulo: Little Baby Bum: Nursery Rhyme Friends
Enredo: Twinkle, Mia, Jacus and the rest of the Nursery Rhyme Friends perform catchy tunes for the little ones.
Kids rule in a place called Harvey Street, where a trio of girls right wrongs, ice cream is always an option, and every day feels like Saturday.
The Buddis bounce, spin, glide — and giggle! — through their magical world, learning new things and sharing the joy of friendship.
Revenge, passion and dark secrets push a successful fashion designer and single mother to her limits when she meets a handsome and mysterious man.
Five girls from India's most impoverished families attend a boarding school designed to create opportunities as they strive for a brighter future.
Six stand-ups explore the coarse and salacious side of comedy in this series of half-hour specials. For mature audiences.
Inspired by the classic novel, this telenovela follows Heidi, who leaves her happy life in the mountains behind when her aunt takes her to the big city.
Go behind the scenes with social media sensation Cameron Dallas as he takes his career to the next level on an international tour.
Country artist Coffey Anderson and his wife, hip-hop dancer Criscilla, juggle family life, career goals and tests of faith in this reality series.
Lovable pug Chip starts kindergarten, makes new friends and tries new things – with a little help from Potato, her secret mouse pal.
After crossing paths at a crime scene, a renowned math teacher and an antiques appraiser embark on an unexpected journey of love and self-discovery.
K-pop star Seungri, BIGBANG's youngest member, tries to lead a team of bumbling staff at YG's Future Strategy Office in this mockumentary sitcom.
People bring their stories of missed lust connections to an objective panel of experts who then judge whether they could have gone all the way or not.
After an accident leads to great weight loss, once-obese Mi Duo embarks on a new life working for her secret crush, diamond company CEO Xiao Liang.
Cookie, Pudding and Candy are kitten siblings whose favorite things are sweet treats and letting their curiosity lead them on adventures in learning.
Staying at home doesn't mean sitting still for energetic Bo and her little dragon friend Dezzy, who embark on amazing adventures through movement.
Years after a wealthy man is healed by a rural herbalist, fate lands him in the same hospital where the woman's granddaughter is treating patients.

Titulo: How to Live Mortgage Free with Sarah Beeny
Enredo: Real estate expert and TV presenter Sarah Beeny meets with clever property owners who share their colorful stories about living mortgage free.
In a social experiment, a group of daughters sends their mothers, disguised as 21-year-olds, into the world to experience life as a member of Gen Z.
Inspired by Khon dance drama and Thai martial arts, a fighter scarred by the past joins forces with a determined cop to battle an organized crime ring.
Three films chronicle the cocaine trade's sweeping impact on the citizens of Peru, Brazil and Colombia, from poor farmers to powerful drug lords.
After a chance meeting at a ballpark, the kind son of a former gangster tries to help an outgoing radio DJ get over her recent heartbreak.
In this fast-paced, high-energy karaoke competition, singers from all walks of life battle it out for up to 30,000 euros!

Titulo: In The Bosom of a Thorn

Enredo: In an underwater village bordering a tropical island, two young turtles and their pals keep their home safe and enjoy adventures in the big, wild sea.
The lives of five strangers become intertwined forever when a starlet filming a documentary is kidnapped on the streets of Hong Kong.
Home cooks try – and inevitably fail – to re-create spectacular confections on this comical competition show, all for a sweet 5,000 euros.
In a series of magical missions, quick-witted YooHoo and his can-do crew travel the globe to help animals in need.
In a luxurious condominium complex with draconian rules forbidding all romance, two residents fall in love and dare to start a secret relationship.
Rising India-based comics Prashasti Singh, Kaneez Surka, Supriya Joshi and Niveditha Prakasam bring no-holds-barred humor to this stand-up series.
Go behind the scenes with Brazilian pop icon Anitta, along with her friends and family, as she aims to create a new song and music video each month.
Whether styling superstars or elevating A-list homes, couple Jason Bolden and Adair Curtis of JSN Studio connect famous clientele with the chicest looks.
Trotro the donkey may be opinionated, but he's as sweet as can be in this animated series that's full of lessons for children.
Masha explains why there's no need to be scared of things like monsters, the dark, going to a new school, thunder and other common childhood fears.
In a tale of bravery and heroism, fearless frogs go to war against the sinister scorpions and spiders that have teamed up to conquer the amphibians.
In a world known as the Copper Dimension, a group of high-school girls fights against dark forces – and their own inner demons.
The Philippine jail known for a viral Michael Jackson dance video comes under the management of an ex-convict, sparking controversy and criticism.
An ambitious, talented politician embarks on an intense journey toward winning the presidency while juggling his complicated family affairs.
A bright and spirited seven-year-old girl uses her vivid, dreamlike imagination to navigate everyday adventures alongside her real and imaginary BFFs.
When the children of two families become friends, they begin to unravel a horrific crime in the past that already linked their fathers to each other.
Before one of them moves to the U.S., two childhood friends promise to reunite as adults. But illness and the vagaries of the heart stand in the way.

Titulo: Frank Elstner: Just One Last Question
Enredo: In his farewell show, legendary German host Frank Elstner digs deep and savors his discussions with stars such as Daniel Brühl and Lena Meyer-Landrut.
When a hard-nosed detective reluctantly partners with an informant to solve complex cases, she uncovers links to a particularly puzzling cold case.
Gifted with special powers, fighting skills and slick hair, the rowdy KO One navigates tough friendships and high school romance.
Now the Blue Sky King, Darel must lead a rescue mission to save a Dream Walker – leaving the village under the protection of the Kulipari youth.
Zenos wants to use the Earth’s negative energy for his own good – and it's up to Miniforce X to stop this space alien’s evil plans.
When a wardrobe malfunction goes viral, a bubbly live streamer struggles to navigate her classmates' cruel judgment and the small town she lives in.
In the Silver Dimension, Liu Bei, Guan Yu and Zhang Fei plan to enroll in an elite academy as sworn brothers, but KO One visitors derail the plan.
Two young stars with different backgrounds and agendas enter into a fake marriage to advance their careers, until the fake starts turning real.
Sports and friendship intertwine in tales of a volleyball team, an autistic badminton player, a skateboarder with depression and an archery-club crush.
Rascal Flatts bassist Jay DeMarcus and ex-beauty queen Allison DeMarcus write their own rules for juggling family and fun in this reality show.
Facing disapproving parents, a knotty love life and her own inner critic, an aspiring comic ditches her cushy but unsatisfying life to pursue stand-up.
Little Mila turns playtime into a series of fun and educational adventures with her magical pet Morphle, who transforms into anything she dreams up!
BFFs Wesley and Georgie and their silly cat sidekick Pretzel transform into ninjas and enter a magic world, where they solve problems and save the day.
A by-the-book police captain and a brash young detective must team up to take on the supernatural when strange forces begin to wreak havoc on Dakar.
An assortment of talent takes the stage for a night of honest stand-up featuring four of Mexico's funniest LGBTQ comedians.
For a group of charismatic undergraduates, the jolting revelations from a campus blog turn surviving university life into a serious matter.
A series of mysterious text messages from the future sends ripples through the lives of a delivery woman and an accomplished cyclist.
Love and intrigue swirl around two women – one a champion of human rights, the other an ambitious businesswoman – who were switched at birth.
Beloved children's book character Llama Llama springs to life in this heartwarming series about family, friendship and learning new things.
After taking a break from the business, a music producer returns with a new project in mind: launching a co-ed pop idol group.
Two women at a cosmetics company compete for love and success. One uses her brain and diligence, while the other works her beauty and charm.
Three years after making a wild promise to a woman in distress, a rigid businessman runs into her again and must decide whether to honor his word.
Love leaps off the page when an astronomer magically meets her comic book hero in the flesh, but learns that his fictional problems are very real.

Titulo: The Sound of Your Heart: Reboot
Enredo: Webtoonist Cho Seok is back with more anecdotes of mix-ups, unintended antics, and bathroom blunders in this reboot starring an all-new cast.
A young horse enthusiast teams up with her best friends to rescue and rehabilitate animals on her family's beloved ranch.

Titulo: Bangkok รัก Stories 2 ตอน ไม่เดียงสา

Enredo: A veteran cop forms an agency dedicated to solving cold cases, including those related to the team members' own painful and mysterious pasts.

Titulo: Love for Ten: Generation of Youth
Enredo: A nerdy engineering student falls for a pretty, outgoing girl at his college. To get closer to her, he joins the theater group she belongs to.
These Mexico City socialites may lead opulent lives, but a peek behind the curtain reveals a tangled web of intrigue, envy and personal struggles.
A bright-eyed girl and her magical owl sidekick find adventure when enchanting powers and creative ideas lead to important lessons.
Three grown siblings must rethink their idea of family when they learn their parents are getting divorced and have their eyes on new partners.
Four female friends in the fast-paced city of Lagos, Nigeria endure public and private pressures to walk down the aisle by the age of 30.
Twenty years after their debut, join the beloved members of Arashi on a new journey as they showcase their lives, talents and gifts to the world.
This docuseries spotlights Afro-Brazilian thinkers sharing their individual journeys and discussing representation, entrepreneurship and community.
The fun-loving Gumbles bounce and play while staying away from the foul-smelling Bottersnikes who live in a nearby junkyard.
From decorating his home to devouring sweets, join Bheem as he makes merry – and a bit of mischief – while the festival of lights is in full swing.
A group of reality stars transitions into their newly achieved fame while dealing with the demands of an obnoxious TV executive and their regular lives.
In this social drama of sin and remorse, a man reels at the discovery that his wife has been unfaithful, and gives her an ultimatum.
Through the magic of the Story Spinner, True and her friends create their own versions of Pinocchio, Little Red Riding Hood and other classic tales.
An unfortunate accident alters the life of a high school basketball prodigy, who abandons his beloved sport and becomes entangled in a love triangle.
Tiny grocery store items come to life as the Shopkins, who have fun adventures with each other at Small Mart and the magical town called Shopville.
In this karaoke competition hosted by Palina Rojinski, contestants must hit the right note for a chance to win up to 30,000 euros.
With help from her magic toy chest, fun-loving Luna Petunia enters the fantastic land of Amazia, where adventures, friendship and learning await.
Three 30-something women in high-level jobs at a beauty e-commerce firm seem to have it all – except when it comes to love and romantic chemistry.
Leading astronomers reveal the latest discoveries about death-trap planets, asteroids, comets and other wonders of the cosmos.
A mysterious, wealthy man offers three people a lucrative, unusual job that may be too good to be true: Live the high life as his children and heirs.
This relatable relationship drama explores the real-life trials and joys of married life through the lens of 11 different wives.
From scientists to snake handlers, this series explores what motivates some people to put themselves in jeopardy to perform extraordinary feats.
When their animal friends need help, brother-and-sister team Toby and Teri use the clues and follow the facts to solve mysteries in their own backyard.
Diagnosed with a condition that could make her infertile, a career woman must choose one of four bachelors to make a baby with before time runs out.
She's the most unlikely candidate to ever stumble into the role of a reporter, and she’s keeping everyone on their toes with her eccentric ways.

Titulo: Jimmy: The True Story of a True Idiot
Enredo: In the 1980s, a simple-minded fool named Hideaki meets comedy legend Sanma, changes his name to Jimmy and becomes a comedic superstar.
A detective and a psychologist investigating a string of murders form a crime-solving team with the novelist whose work inspired the killings.
Peer into the lives of young Singaporeans as they defy expectations and traverse the tricky terrain of career, romance and family.
After years in the U.S., a Taiwanese immigrant returns to her hometown with a young daughter in tow to assist her father with his bed-and-breakfast.
Two renowned culinary families led by legendary food icons battle for the position of greatest chef, while protecting their secret kimchee recipes.
This Complex series follows the paper trail of musicians and athletes in Los Angeles as they blow through stacks on the finer things in life.
A boy and his homemade robot enter the toughest competition in the universe while attempting to free their oppressed home from an evil empire.
Two lonely singles meet on a blind date and slowly get to know each other, unaware that their parents are friends and may be falling in love.
When laidback Ren, who is about to divorce his money-crazy wife, finds a time-traveling computer, he decides to use it to reboot his marriage.
After reconnecting with their girlhood crushes, two sisters find their lives turned upside down by surprising revelations and romantic intrigue.
When it comes to daring stunts and outrageous pranks, we often wonder: What were they thinking? This high-octane series tries to find some answers.
Sing along and dance with Bailey, Franny, Kip, Lulu and Tilly in this collection of music videos that will get you in the mood to move and groove!
Reminiscing about his youth in Taiwan's turbulent 1920s, Guo Xuehu reflects on his passion for art, a friendship with a painter – and a doomed romance.
Follow Santiago Artemis, a Buenos Aires fashion dynamo, as he makes his dreams come true while grappling with his love life, therapist and clients.
Living under the same roof, a group of unabashed friends wrestle with everyday issues from financial woes and shared quarters to romantic misfires.
On this competition show, novice bakers try to avoid a fiasco while duplicating stunning sweets. At stake are a trophy and 5,000 euros.
What's in your fridge? In sunny Refrigerator Land, everyday ingredients transform into animal friends who love a good adventure.

Titulo: The Year of Happiness and Love
Enredo: Jiang Chen-bo is a loser without prospects for success, until a surprise promotion becomes the catalyst for his entire family's upturn in fortune.
Amidst poverty and struggle, a hardened pantsula dance leader enters a dark space and searches for redemption and salvation in his community.
Sang-ah would do anything to shield pop star Ah-shin from rabid fans. But after an act of protection gone wrong, it looks like she's the crazy one.
Young beetle Dylan and his friends Hailey and Ollie team up to compete against tough opponents in the exciting, high-octane sport of Battle Blading.
A brave, energetic little boy with superhuman powers leads his friends on exciting adventures to guard their fellow Dholakpur villagers from evil.
Four comedians from Brazil riff on sexuality, politics, religion and motherhood – and set out to prove a woman's place is anywhere she wants it to be.
An army deserter hiding out in a small coastal town becomes the coach of a youth baseball team and develops warm relationships in his new community.
In Colombia in 1821, a white orphan is taken in by black slaves. Years after being torn from them, she returns to find her family and childhood love.
Despite his heroics, security guard Richard Jewell becomes a suspect in the FBI investigation of a foiled terrorist attack at the 1996 Olympics.

Titulo: The Great British Baking Show: Holidays
Enredo: Deck the halls with sugar, butter and chocolate as competitors from past seasons bake sweet Yuletide treats for judges Paul Hollywood and Prue Leith.

Titulo: Trailer Park Boys: Out of the Park: USA
